{"tid":1342213,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[急]明日緊急罷工罷課","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:02.000Z","uid":255437,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"daf5b39b9e96f42c6995e219b471e44506c16560","tid":1342213,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"緊急發起明天罷市罷工罷課，<br />\n理由係今晚元朗發生的事件，<br />\n顯示香港政府同香港警察已經無能力保障市民生命財產安全，<br />\n現呼籲全港市民發起三罷，<br />\n直至政府及警察為事件作出交代，<br />\n包括：<br />\n<br />\n1）全數緝拿涉事兇徒歸案<br />\n2）全盤交代警力不足及遲遲不到現場原因，追究一切相關人事責任<br />\n3）因應有市民拍到立法會、議員何君堯於事發前與疑似元朗黑道中人相約面談，要求徹查何於事件中的角色！<br />\n<br />\n以上三項，缺一回應，堅持無限期三罷！<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳轉發！"},{"pid":"5845d826f0b3b947dd9b6651d01354091f556c25","tid":1342213,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b5348f921d9ad5e50c27e144d05c65f8f8d455","tid":1342213,"uid":219528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ad8b2e61da7130d8ece4ff27d2a4a114180f302","tid":1342213,"uid":219528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eed36b2f9cff274715e22f377267d7cbdab322a9","tid":1342213,"uid":113800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:25:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f9991924d4cffd1782d94f914980bfe34148cb0d","tid":1342213,"uid":276176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c78c9f05f633adaadc19d0f16480322854a2c5d7","tid":1342213,"uid":219528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n希望成事"},{"pid":"da3a8174f16a5a79070a49aa23d1d039772c844c","tid":1342213,"uid":223198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c78c9f05f633adaadc19d0f16480322854a2c5d7","tid":1342213,"uid":219528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n希望成事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"eada43da3511c5390d90d6926d912adabca2bfe0","tid":1342213,"uid":81149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8ca45a4f36bb0e5c4020befe9f1732b07871bdb","tid":1342213,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:53:34.000Z","msg":"利申，我係一個打工仔<br />\n之前有幾次都想三罷，但因為根本其他人有照返工，結果我都逼住要返<br />\n<br />\n認真，唔洗理乜柒民意，搵人去塞下地鐵<br />\n交通癱左自然全香港會一齊同你罷工<br />\n<br />\n罷工幾星期，港共政權一定會跪"},{"pid":"4c4c9bb1058f56bacfacfc5857d22b698d8d8eed","tid":1342213,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}